msgid "{note} The Argon2i driver requires PHP 7.2.0 or greater and the Argon2id driver requires PHP 7.3.0 or greater."
msgstr "{note} Argon2i Driver 需要 PHP 最低版本 7.2.0，Argon2id Driver 需要 PHP 最低版本 7.3.0。"

